How coindesk_scraper works:

user types coindesk_scraper

show a list of most recent news

# Title - Time - URL

"Which news article would you want to read more about?"

User input: # or key words or exit

Output: 
- #
  - the according news article
    - option to exit, read next, or go back to the list page or key words?

- key words
  - list of articles: # Title - Time - URL (how do i search within the articles too?)
    - ask for # to read more or return back to the list or exit
      - if #: option to return one level up or exit